## DB tables (Supabase) — full schema in PRD.md Section 9

`profiles` `sessions` `anubhav` `sacred_moments`
`user_milestones` `city_seeds` `feedback` `research_log`

Never create tables or columns outside this schema without flagging first.

---

## Session hygiene — required

After every coding session:
1. Update `SETUP_LOG.md` — what was done, what's next, any blockers
2. New decisions made → add to `DECISIONS.md`
3. Research used → verify `RESEARCH_PIPELINE.md` is current
4. `git add . && git commit -m "..." && git push origin main`

This is how nothing gets lost between sessions.
